    94→ *
    95→ * <p><strong>Thread Safety:</strong> Instances are immutable after construction and safe for concurrent read access.
    96→ * The {@link MutableRecordBatch} interface allows in-place updates for broker-side operations (e.g., timestamp
    97→ * rewriting during log compaction), but these updates should only be performed under exclusive synchronization.
    98→ *
